  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate long-term treatment with Zomacton® for pituitary
      short stature in children with insufficient growth hormone production and/or short stature
      caused by Turner syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
